tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE solar_panel_efficiency (
    panel_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    location TEXT,
    installation_date DATE,
    efficiency_percentage DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE efficiency_logs ( 
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    panel_id INT, 
    recorded_date TIMESTAMP, 
    efficiency_measurement FLOAT, 
    FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES solar_panels(panel_id) 
 );

CREATE TABLE SolarPanelEfficiency (
    panel_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    installation_date DATE,
    efficiency DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE SolarPanelEfficiency (
    panel_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    efficiency FLOAT,
    installation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE PanelLocation (
    panel_id INT,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_panel_id FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES SolarPanelEfficiency(panel_id)
)

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceLog (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    description TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_panel_id FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES SolarPanelEfficiency(panel_id)
)

CREATE TABLE WeatherData (
    observation_date DATE,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE PanelRatings (
    panel_id INT,
    rating INT,
    review TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_panel_id FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES SolarPanelEfficiency(panel_id)
)
